5|$|In PC Magazine testing, Norton {{detected}} 15 of 16 spyware samples. 13 of the 16 were removed. Against eight commercial <b>keyloggers,</b> {{the suite}} removed all the samples. On a clean system, Norton blocked 14 of the 16 spyware samples from installing, and stopped {{seven of the}} eight <b>keyloggers</b> from installing.|$|R
