5000|$|API-based: These keyloggers hook {{keyboard}} APIs {{inside a}} running application. The <b>keylogger</b> registers keystroke events, {{as if it}} was a normal piece of the application instead of malware. The <b>keylogger</b> receives an event each time the user presses or releases a key. The <b>keylogger</b> simply records it.|$|E
